/span></p></blockquote><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"></h3><hr><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/5Uq_c38N_HMV8cLhIL3HH.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(176, 202, 255); color: inherit;\">one scene:</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\">Spencer is picking you up for winter formal despite your dad hating him.</p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/x8aVCAfseHvCPw_WD5HOY.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">You’ve been dating for a few months and your dad— the principal of Coral Springs High— hates him. It’s implied your last name is Whitman but he can be your step-dad sooo. Everything else is entirely up to you.</p><hr><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(224, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">CW/TW:</mark></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"> <mark style=\"background-color: rgb(101, 101, 101); color: inherit;\">Substance reference, disapproving parent, somewhat asshole boyfriend</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/zvDprmP3bN-HI1OlR0W62.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p>— <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/22d3eed4-8ef5-4697-99d9-200fdfdc9395_character-spencer-miller\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>He climbs through your window</strong></a></p><p>— <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https:/